{"tid":2131700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"居中國老翁不滿政府未押後立法會選舉 入稟高等法院並要求法庭下令鄭月娥押後選舉","createTime":"2020-07-30T04:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T05:34:45.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6c52b15fc7fd9a5e2a7ff5cd5e8fbb0d2724b840","tid":2131700,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:27:59.000Z","msg":"居於內地的78歲港人昨日入稟高等法院提請司法覆核，指鑑於「第三波」冠狀病毒疫情，政府決定於9月6日舉行立法會選舉投票屬不合理，要求政府押後選舉。他自言是20多萬居於內地的香港永久性居民之一，是積極的選民，在區議會和立法會投票日會特意回港投票...<br />\n<br />\n本案建議答辯人為行政長官和政制及內地事務局局長。申請書指，申請人譚國源（譯音）並非冠狀病毒防疫措施下的豁免檢疫人士。他於前日（28日）去信特首，要求按照法例盡可能押後投票，直至解除所有抗疫措施為止...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/TOBX6YPQX6EEJBBLOG4UUQSO44/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FTOBX6YPQX6EEJBBLOG4UUQSO44%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=3b7ecec7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FTOBX6YPQX6EEJBBLOG4UUQSO44%2F&h=c1cdc3bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/TOBX6YPQX6EEJBBLOG4UUQSO44/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d9e19819b7aa2c595de6352d9860bddf907c38","tid":2131700,"uid":141668,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:29:05.000Z","msg":"係唔係要覆核下佢嘅選民資格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b19a645037083ecb912dd9043d1db339c41f850","tid":2131700,"uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:29:41.000Z","msg":"唔係長居香港冇資格做選民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8844eca4761d6db334fa31eb6f8adec57566899d","tid":2131700,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係長期居住香港無權投票"},{"pid":"9f65274ae1d48bc25fd600fdd94403c2